how do we react?

09:11.217 --> 09:16.346
- She's got to be better than Emanuela.
- Don't even mention her name!

09:16.472 --> 09:20.225
- Who's Emanuela?
- Peppe's ex-wife.

09:20.351 --> 09:22.978
- She was anything but pretty.
- No.

09:23.604 --> 09:27.857
Now that it's all over
I gotta say that hoarse voice of hers

09:28.067 --> 09:30.485
