09:31.946 --> 09:34.239
It was before...

09:34.448 --> 09:37.576
You're saying it was after?
I wouldn't be so sure.

09:37.868 --> 09:40.120
- But she was strange.
- Yes.

09:41.247 --> 09:43.623
It's not bad, this bio...

09:45.501 --> 09:47.002
They're here!

09:57.388 --> 10:00.640
Good evening, everyone.
Hi, guys.

10:04.145 --> 10:05.520
- What's up?
- Where's Lucilla?

10:05.896 --> 10:07.522
