10:08.024 --> 10:11.985
- So she's not coming?
- No, she has a fever.

10:12.236 --> 10:16.156
- We really wanted to meet her.
- I know, she's disappointed too.

10:18.659 --> 10:21.286
- Do you want me to go?
- No!

10:21.871 --> 10:25.123
- How are you?
- Fine, thanks.

10:27.627 --> 10:31.171
- She's ditched you already.
- Don't start that.

10:31.297 --> 10:33.256
- Did you two fight?
- No.

10:33.549 --> 10:36.426
- How old did you say she was?
- I didn't say.

10:36.636 --> 10:39.304
- But she's our age.
- Ouch!

10:39.513 --> 10:42.015
- What?
- She's old then.

10:42.183 --> 10:46.394
- It's a mature relationship.
- We said no jokes about Lucilla.

10:47.063 --> 10:49.314
- No, it's for Peppe.
- Thanks.

10:49.523 --> 10:51.316
- But Lucilla's not here.
- Right.

10:51.567 --> 10:55.528
But I am.
And you were saying... what?

10:55.655 --> 10:57.530
- The usual things.
- Such as?

10:57.907 --> 11:01.660
Just... we don't know her,
so we were trying to guess.

11:02.036 --> 11:04.037
Will she be tall, short...

11:04.163 --> 11:08.166
The usual, no...
Is she a redhead, brunette...

11:08.334 --> 11:11.336
- Blond.
- We even thought she might be gray.

11:11.462 --> 11:13.463
- Gray?
- Yes.

11:13.589 --> 11:15.090
Leave him alone!

11:15.466 --> 11:18.301
- Come on, the eclipse has started.
- Let's go!

11:18.928 --> 11:20.970
- I can see two.
- There are two.

11:21.180 --> 11:24.599
- I can see two because I can't see.
- Use this to focus it...

11:24.975 --> 11:27.686
Now I can see it! It's lovely.

11:29.188 --> 11:31.481
Lucilla's a nice name.

11:31.607 --> 11:34.359
