- You study these things.

11:50.751 --> 11:54.754
I'll tell you. If you talk to her
for 30 minutes a day, you're in love.

11:55.089 --> 11:59.134
- What if I talk for 60 minutes?
- Then you're madly in love.

11:59.510 --> 12:02.137
