which means you're married.

12:02.263 --> 12:06.516
- How long have you been together?
- Awhile, a few months.

12:06.642 --> 12:10.478
Great! The first sparks.
Are you ablaze?

12:11.105 --> 12:12.522
- Are you?
- I'm ablaze.

12:12.732 --> 12:14.399
- He's ablaze.
- I'm ablaze.

12:14.525 --> 12:17.527
Why did you choose tonight
to introduce us?

12:17.737 --> 12:20.530
I didn't choose, it just happened.

12:20.656 --> 12:23.992
Do you remember the evening
I met you all?

12:25.536 --> 12:28.288
- I was so anxious!
- Why?

12:28.414 --> 12:32.667
- She was so tense, poor girl.
- Meeting Cosimo's friends!

12:32.793 --> 12:35.670
All for this sweet deal here...

12:36.046 --> 12:39.382
From that point of view,
Lucilla wasn't worried.

12:39.508 --> 12:41.551
- Lucky her.
- That's why she has a fever!

12:43.763 --> 12:46.514
- I changed outfits 10 times that day.
- 20.

12:46.807 --> 12:52.187
