I feel like one of the gang now.

12:52.313 --> 12:55.190
- Who, you?
- One of the gang?

12:55.441 --> 12:57.442
No way!

12:59.195 --> 13:02.530
Darling, look at their faces.
They're teasing.

13:03.073 --> 13:05.658
- They're teasing.
- Of course we are.

13:05.826 --> 13:09.454
- You're our favorite.
- Cosimo, you got lucky.

13:09.580 --> 13:12.332
