14:49.179 --> 14:52.181
- Peppe's right.
- All right, but I'm warning you.

14:52.308 --> 14:55.435
If Cosimo cheats on me,
I want you to tell me.

14:55.644 --> 14:57.562
- If you really want to know...
- Idiot.

14:57.771 --> 15:01.691
- They'd never give each other away.
- They're all the same.

15:01.901 --> 15:04.444
- A losing battle.
- We're too different.

15:04.570 --> 15:06.946
Like a PC and a Mac.

15:07.698 --> 15:10.199
- And what are men?
- A PC, obviously.

15:10.409 --> 15:13.786
