Intuitive, fast, elegant.

15:27.927 --> 15:30.470
Expensive and compatible
only among themselves.

15:30.846 --> 15:33.348
Yes, but they're addictive too.

15:34.725 --> 15:38.186
- What will happen to Diego now?
- Nothing.

15:38.354 --> 15:41.731
- He's got no wife and kids.
