- Just ask Peppe.

15:56.747 --> 16:01.626
I'm no example, my wife
nearly had to pay me alimony.

16:02.628 --> 16:06.965
A lawyer, however despicable,
knows how much a P.E. teacher earns.

16:07.466 --> 16:12.512
