16:23.399 --> 16:27.402
No, but he could've at least
deleted the text...

16:27.528 --> 16:30.405
He was screwing a young girl,
he should've been careful.

16:30.531 --> 16:33.866
- What?
- Should've been careful about what?

16:34.034 --> 16:38.913
