16:40.499 --> 16:43.793
Lele, pass me the eggplant patties.
It's hot!

16:44.420 --> 16:47.922
Cosimo's right,
you do have to be careful.

16:51.427 --> 16:56.889
We have everything in here.
It's the black box of our lives.

16:57.057 --> 17:01.519
How many couples would split up
if they looked at each other's phones?

17:06.400 --> 17:08.818
