17:17.453 --> 17:19.954
What's the problem?
Here, take it.

17:21.040 --> 17:22.832
- Oh I will.
- Go ahead.

17:23.541 --> 17:25.710
Lele, cut that out.

17:25.919 --> 17:28.588
- Look, his hand's trembling.
- He's turned pale.

17:28.797 --> 17:32.300
