17:41.977 --> 17:45.855
- Would you let Cosimo have yours?
- I don't even have a passcode.

17:45.981 --> 17:49.692
Darling, I wouldn't want yours.

17:49.818 --> 17:52.612
Rocco would rather swallow his,
wouldn't you, love?

17:52.738 --> 17:56.866
